  <brief_title>Trial Comparing Different Medical Devices for Infragenual Dilatation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomised Comparing Trial Between an Infragenual Dilatation (ID), an ID With Stenting, an ID With Cutting Balloon and Laser Therapy</official_title>
